channel.title: WahnScape
channel.description: I recently Joined a server called WahnScape, Very good server could do with more players so i thought i would post on here to advertise it, please log in and give it a try and you might find the server you have been waiting for, has Lord Marshalls have been added into game. COOL BOSSES LIKE: Nomad Avatar of destruction (Drops Primal and Chaotics) KBD Sea Troll Queen (Drops Spirit Shields) Corp Beast (Drops Sigils) then use them with a blessed spirit shield which you can get from the Level Shop for 700 points! It is being updated and new things brought daily please go to www.wahnscape.com and download client to play.. My ingame name is Artz Skillz, so log in and say Artz Skillz sent you :)
